1. *Sjedni* na stolicu i pričaj sa mnom. (Sit down* on the chair and talk to me.)
2. Mogu li *sjesti* kraj tebe? (Can I *sit* next to you?)
3. Molim te, *sjedni* ovdje i pričekaj me. (Please, *sit* here and wait for me.)
4. Moramo *sjesti* i razgovarati o ovome. (We need to *sit* down and talk about this.)
5. Nisam mogao *sjesti* jer je stolica bila slomljena. (I couldn't *sit* because the chair was broken.)
6. *Sjednite* u automobil i krenimo. ( *Sit* in the car and let's go.)
7. Čim sam ušao u kuću, *sjeo* sam na kauč. (As soon as I entered the house, I *sat* on the couch.)
8. *Sjedi* ravno, ne pogrbljuj se. ( *Sit* straight, don't slouch.)
9. Ne mogu *sjesti* jer mi je previše hladno. (I can't *sit* because it's too cold.)
10. *Sjedila* je na klupi i čitala knjigu. (She *was sitting* on the bench and reading a book.)